videos.headline: Davin Zeigler's desperation 3 sends Green Bay to OT vs. Milwaukee
videos.description: Davin Zeigler knocks down the tough 3-pointer with a little over a second remaining for Green Bay to send the game to overtime.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Davin Zeigler's desperation 3 sends Green Bay to OT vs. Milwaukee) 2023/02/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Davin Zeigler ends Green Bay's 14-game losing streak with an OT Jumper
videos.description: Davin Zeigler knocks down the jumper with a little over a second remaining in overtime for the win, snapping Green Bay's 14-game losing streak.
